- "Minimum and maximum total values" are calculated within each category and are used to filter the products.

- "Shining stars" refers to the top 2 products by sales rank;
- "Reaped the highest sales" means the products with the highest total sales;
- "Average rating of their suppliers" means the average rating of the suppliers who provide these top products.

